subject: Your Christmas Wish List
content: Hi! I received your Christmas wish list. I'll do my best to bring your favorite toys!

subject: Homework Reminder
content: Don't forget to finish your math homework before dinner!

subject: Great Job on Science Project!
content: Your volcano project was amazing! You got an A+!

subject: Playdate This Weekend?

content: I'm sending you a special surprise for your birthday!

subject: Can I Have a Pet?
content: Please can I get a puppy? I promise to take care of it!

subject: Thanks for the Playdate
content: Thanks for having me over! The LEGO set was awesome!
